{"tid":134590,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"GiGi 宣 佈 年 尾 追 第 二 胎","createTime":"2017-02-25T15:00:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-25T15:04:07.000Z","uid":35964,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5998dc95b4ef67503ab6e12cfd8658c1cd6bf42c","tid":134590,"uid":35964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T15:00:32.000Z","msg":"梁詠琪（GiGi）日前為電影《骨妹》在旺角接受訪問，她慨嘆拍此片時是人生體重高峯期，她說：「拍攝時剛餵完人奶，因為劇本吸引唔好嘥，肥少少唔緊要，當時比𠵱家肥二十幾磅，睇番都有少少嚇親。」<br />\n另外，GiGi計劃年尾再懷第二胎，她說：「我哋已決定咗想喺年尾，年中會做巡迴演唱會part2，八至十場，下次一定收咗身先再拍戲。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20170225/large/25ec3p2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170225%2Flarge%2F25ec3p2.jpg&h=c45595ce&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"638f7dd0ee71740f3b3194e4ef9a2ee7d64125fa","tid":134590,"uid":35637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T15:01:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">s</span></span>"},{"pid":"90c3d53f27aca68a65c6abf11a79d12c9f968969","tid":134590,"uid":7846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T15:04:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}